<%= render "shared/header"%>
<header class="lg:bg-home bg-home-phone bg-cover bg-left lg:bg-top h-screen-4/5 flex flex-col justify-center lg:justify-end">
  <div class="w-full flex justify-end text-white">
    <div class="flex flex-col max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-bold text-5xl lg:text-6xl pb-5 lg:px-0 px-5">Aircraft Management</h1>
      <p class="pb-10 tracking-tight px-0 mr-20 hidden lg:block">
      We recognize that owning an aircraft is a substantial investment with significant responsibilities. When you choose Penn Jet to assist in the management of your aircraft, you access a comprehensive suite of services centered around safety, service, and support. Our commitment to overseeing your aviation assets enables you to fully enjoy the advantages of your investment. Unlock flexibility, convenience, and reliability with Penn Jet aircraft management services.
      </p>
      <p class="lg:hidden px-5">
      When you choose Penn Jet to support the operation of your aircraft, you get a full range of services focused on Safety, Service and Savings.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

</header>

<section class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row bg-blue-900 text-white" id="about">
  <div class="lg:w-1/2 py-10 lg:py-20 flex-col items-center">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl pb-12 px-5">Your Trusted Aircraft Management Partner</h2>
    <p class="px-5 leading-relaxed pb-10">
      Experience the confidence of unmatched safety, steadfast support, and exceptional service with Penn Jet. As your trusted aircraft management partner, we place safety at the core of our operations, ensuring meticulous care and diligence for your aviation asset. 
    </p>
    <p class="px-5 leading-relaxed">
      Beyond safety, our comprehensive support encompasses operational excellence and precise maintenance oversight. With Penn Jet, you're not just a client - you're our priority. We're dedicated to exceeding your service expectations. Choose a partner who is committed to your aircraft's success.
    </p>
    <button class="btn-secondary mx-5 mt-10" onclick="scrollToElement('contact', 30);">
